The Marnie Flook miniature book collection records, consist of material related
                    to Marnie Flook's collection of miniature books. Materials include: invoices;
                    catalogues and prospectuses; correspondence with publishers and book dealers;
                    issues of "The Microbibliophile" (1982-2003); and five issues of
                    "Microbibliotrivia" by Val Poska (1984-1989).
